/h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e15610f34674f02caf174515ea5136d4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Mussomeli1-132x200.jpg" width="66" height="100" alt="Gianguido Mussomeli" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Gianguido Mussomeli"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/gianguido-mussomeli/">View all articles by Gianguido Mussomeli</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/06/ne-congiunga-il-nume-in-ciel-la-lucia-di-lammermoor-di-donizetti-tra-walter-scott-e-romanticismo-cattolico-parte-seconda/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Ne congiunga il nume in Ciel.  La Lucia di Lammermoor di Donizetti tra Walter Scott e romanticismo cattolico (Parte seconda)</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2011/06/trieste-teatro-verdilucia-di-lammermoor/" rel="next">Trieste, Teatro Verdi:&#8221;Lucia di Lammermoor&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2011/06/stoccarda-staatsoperla-juive/#r